Description:
 user-installed-packages - list user installed packages
Changes:
 user-installed-packages (26.06.1) mx; urgency=medium
 .
   * Fix bash completion partial filename cycling (compgen -G -> compgen -f)
   * Fix bash completion: one-tab directory lookahead for uip-list-*.txt files
   * Fix working directory: cd to home when launched from / (desktop entries)
   * Fix uip_confirm: use bash string operators instead of tr for UTF-8 locale chars
   * Fix uip_confirm: show English [Y/n] when question string is not yet translated
   * Fix file chooser: replace eval+find with mapfile
   * Fix quote translated strings in bash -c
   * Fix help: make 'Usage:', 'command', '[options]', 'Commands:', 'Options:'
     and all descriptions translatable
   * Add -v|--version to CLI help output
   * Translations refresh
